    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Through its collections, and related services, specialising in European policy areas, the EC Library connects Commission staff with data, information and knowledge to support them in developing and delivering informed, evidence-based policies for the benefit of EU citizens whilst providing to all those interested a unique insight into the history of EU integration."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001822"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EC_LIBRARY"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EC_LIBRARY"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
